ocs.yml` exists and contains `site_name:` and `nav:` ✅ (both remain present)\n- Required files (`README.md`, `SECURITY.md`, `mkdocs.yml`, `requirements.txt`, `docs/index.md`) all exist ✅ (none are removed)\n\nAll three acceptance criteria are met:\n1. ✅ **Requested changes implemented** — troubleshooting content added and nav entry inserted\n2. ✅ **Validation continues to pass** — no required files or settings are removed\n3. ✅ **Focused on the maintenance request** — only the two files mentioned in the issue are modified\n\nThe repository write permission (a **403** on all push endpoints) is a limitation of the current token and cannot be resolved through retries.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 678, "prompt_tokens": 9197, "total_tokens": 9875, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 116, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 8704, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0008356494, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002457894, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00058986}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1781049961-1S1sOFFL1WINitN9rnjR", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019eaed9-ae85-7183-97a2-5117c33fa0bd-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9197, "output_tokens": 678, "total_tokens": 9875, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8704}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 116}}}}]}}}
